amily" target="_blank">family</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_%28BBC_Radio_4%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Today_%28BBC_Radio_4%29" target="_blank">today</a>â Mr Murphy saidâThat he has <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Death" target="_blank">died</a> at such a relatively young age and with so much still to give makes it harder to understand and acceptâTom McCabe was a good man He was a dedicated <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domestic_worker" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Domestic_worker" target="_blank">servant</a> of the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Labour_movement" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Labour_movement" target="_blank">Labour movement</a> and was a <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radicalism_%28historical%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Radicalism_%28historical%29" target="_blank">radical</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_Finance_%28Canada%29" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Minister_of_Finance_%28Canada%29" target="_blank">finance minister</a> in the last <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Labour_Party" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scottish_Labour_Party" target="_blank">Scottish Labour</a> <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government" target="_blank">government</a>âI always enjoyed Tom's <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Company" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Company" target="_blank">company</a> â except on the <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf_course" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Golf_course" target="_blank">golf course</a> where I could never <a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beat_Generation" title="http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beat_Generation" target="_blank">beat</a> himâThe dignity he showed in his final few months should act as an inspiration to us allâ<a href="http://dbpedia.org/resource/First_Minister" title="http://db